%% Sage Feature Team - architecture flow
%% Source for docs/img/architecture.svg. Edit this, re-render to SVG with:
%%   mmdc -i docs/img/architecture.mermaid -o docs/img/architecture.svg
%% (mmdc = @mermaid-js/mermaid-cli; install with: npm i -g @mermaid-js/mermaid-cli)

flowchart TD
    A[User: feature request] --> B(ProductOwner)
    B --> C[spec.md<br/>epics/EPIC-N.yaml<br/>stories/STORY-N.yaml]
    C --> D{User: APPROVED?}
    D -->|yes| E[Parallel scheduler<br/>max_parallel_workers]

    E --> F[Story 1 worker]
    E --> G[Story 2 worker]
    E --> H[Story N worker]

    F -.->|"TestCreator -> Developer &lt;-&gt; Tester"| F1[Story 1 DONE]
    G -.-> G1[Story 2 DONE]
    H -.-> H1[Story N DONE]

    F1 --> I(EpicVerifier)
    G1 --> I
    H1 --> I

    I --> J{Gate A: tests pass?<br/>Gate B: AC map verifies?<br/>Gate C: cross-story regression OK?}
    J -->|yes| K[Epic VERIFIED]
    J -->|no| L[Reopen failing stories]
    L --> E

    K --> M{More epics?}
    M -->|yes| E
    M -->|no| N[Feature complete]
